svg.text: Find out among your classmates whose birthday is coming up by asking
(Whose birthday is coming up?). Everyone should take
a turn asking that person what he/she likes to eat, drink, and do. Then work as a class to plan
a birthday party together, and decide who will bring what to the party. In Chinese, note down
the day of the party and the things you were assigned to bring.
谢谢大家今天晚上来我家给我姐
过生日！你们都准备带些什么呀？
